N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1808.11 - Duty to comply

State Regulations

It shall be the duty of any person to comply with any
provision of the compact, or the commission's rules, regulations, orders, approvals, docket conditions, or any other requirements of the
commission. Notes
